![Episode100.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578271285419-HIGPX6VLSUWMWAEZF05C/Episode100.jpg)

It's the **100th** episode of the Major Issues Podcast! On this way more laidback episode, the guys think back on past episodes, talk current events and look towards the future of Major Issues and Comicbook Clique! What makes this episode even more special is that it was recored LIVE via Facebook Live meaning the Major Issues guys were able to chat in front of all the fellow Cliquers out there. Join us in this celebration of all things MAJOR and check out episode 100!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience, and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

